headline: SNN Boosts Shoulder Repair Portfolio With Integrity Orthopaedics Deal
summary: SNN expands its Sports Medicine portfolio with Integrity Orthopaedics, adding next-gen Tendon Seam tech to strengthen leadership in shoulder repair.

headline: Here's Why You Should Hold DaVita Stock in Your Portfolio for Now
